• Just another car selfie • 🤳🏼 So I’m on day 183738393, no really that’s how it feels now lol my due date has changed a couple of times so I’m not quite sure when to expect this lil one anymore and it’s making me panic! We went to a baby trade fair yesterday and bought almost the end of the longest shopping list I’ve ever made in my life! Lol (atleast the big stuff) it’s serious stuff guys! And I feel like it never ends. I need to start packing this hospital bag now cause even though she’s due sometime in December, you just never know when the lil missy wants to make her debut. And THAT is making me super nervous! Now for the most important decision what should her first ever outfit be? LOL no pressure!! 😂 #sheidaspregnancy #pregnancyproblems #mamafashionista #minifashionista #sheidafashionista #36weekspregnant

• Have a beautiful evening my loves • 💛🌼 I’m currently waiting for my last scan, so this will be the last time I see my babygirl through a machine! Next time I see her she’ll be out and in my arms!
